If you want to monthly support the EARTH & DUSK media projects and not just AI:

https://www.patreon.com/earthndusk

Discord: https://discord.gg/Da7s8d3KJ7

Hugging Face Link: https://huggingface.co/Duskfallcrew/duskfall-hair-dye-model

Trained on gothic, punk, varied faces, styles, and wigs and such. Prompting must be done in certain ways, or else it gets weird.

MORE EXAMPLES COMING SOON, just ... patience!

VAE IS INCREDIBLY OPTIONAL- We used Hakurei's one, but we're weird. (Yes we used an Anime one, on a photorealistic model so shoot us LOL)

This is going to be SIMILAR but not the same to the VISUAL KEI one, as both data sets shared a couple of the same faces.

  • DO MERGE THIS

  • DO NOT SELL

  • DO NOT LIKE MERGE AND NOT CREDIT

  • If the girls in this model bite you it's not our fault.
